                    "stepText": "Moving on, a key relation for lenses is provided in the problem. Which of the following formulas is correctly used to relate the focal length $!$f$!$, the object distance $!$u$!$, and the image distance $!$v$!$?",
                    "stepText2": "",
                    "stepImage": "",
                    "stepSolveAnswer": [
                        ""
                    ],
                    "stepSolveAnswerUnits": "",
                    "stepConcepts": [],
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "optionText": "$!$\\frac{1}{f} = \\frac{1}{u} - \\frac{1}{v}$!$",
                            "optionImage": "",
                            "isCorrect": true
